#DIFFERENT TYPES OF CHARTS:
    -lineplot: 
        *tell in a story over time
        *shows trends in data
    -scatter plots
        *x and y coordinate
        *corrilation
    -histograms
        *display of distribution
        *putting things into a bin
        *bell curves
        *very critical on backend
    -bar charts: 
        *proportionality
    -pie charts: 
        *not the most useful
        *tend to avoid

examples:
https://matplotlib.org/3.3.3/gallery/index.html
https://matplotlib.org/3.3.3/tutorials/introductory/sample_plots.html
