Lineplot:
-plot y versus x as lines
-trend line over time or over a series of values
-plt.plot(x,y)
*** Jupyter Notebook: notes_lineplot***

Scatterplots:
-explore relationshiip or correlation between two numeric variables
-plt.scatter()
**** Jupyter Notebook: notes_scatterplot

Histograms:
-plt.hist()
-creates bins for everything
-need to know distribution of your data
